### Flow summary (for your investigation)

| Piece | Role |
|--------|------|
| **Home (`index.tsx`)** | Loader uses `getDashboardPageData` (dashboard server module). Campaign creation is gated by `currentTenant?.tenant_type === "org"`. Multiple CTAs call `openCreateCampaignModal`, which opens `CreateCampaignModal`. |
